data.enText: a rule or principle that most people believe to be true

simple_means.memory_skill: axi 有价值 + om → 有价值的理论 → 公理

tr: (logic) a proposition that is not susceptible of proof or disproof
its truth is assumed to be self-evident
a saying that is widely accepted on its own merits

value.def: An axiom is a statement or idea which people accept as being true.

example.ex: ...the long-held axiom that education leads to higher income.
example.tran: 教育会带来高收入这一长期公认的观念

partsOfSpeech.dec: axi 有价值 + ology …学 → 价值论
axiolo 价值论 + ical …的 → 价值论的
axiolog 价值论 + ist 信仰某种主义的人 → 价值论者
axi 有价值 + om → 有价值的理论 → 公理
axiom 公里 + atic 有…性质的 → 公理不言自明 → 不言自明的
